          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "SYNCH"
                ],
                "institute": "1USANAL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Proton irradiation at 120 GeV was",
                "performed at the Fermi National Accelerator Laboratory"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2JPNOSA"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Proton irradiation at 392 MeV was",
                "performed at Ring Cyclotron of Research Center for",
                "Nuclear Physics, Osaka University,"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP",
                "AMS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After irradiation, the target samples",
                "were prepared chemically for the AMS measurements.",
                "Samples were dissolved in HNO3 after adding 200 mu-g",
                "of Be and 500 mu-g of Al carriers. The Y was firstly",
                "precipitated from its solutions as Y2(C2O4)3 by",
                "adding oxalic acid. The Be and Al were separated by",
                "cation exchange (Dowex 50WX8,100 - 200 mesh) using 1 M",
                "HCl and 1.5 M HCl, respectively. The isotopic ratios",
                "of 10Be/9Be and 26Al/27Al in the Y and Tb target",
                "foils were determined by AMS at MALT (Micro Analysis",
                "Laboratory, Tandem accelerator), University of Tokyo",
                "From the Cu sample, the target element was removed by",
                "anion exchange.Isotopic ratio of 10Be/9Be and 26Al/27Al",
                "was determined by atomic mass spectroscopy."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainties (+-1sigma) quoted in the",
                "production cross sections were obtained by adding",
                "quadratically the uncertainties in the AMS and proton",
                "fluence measurements."
              ]
            },
